    // ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Row 39: Separator ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
    table.cell(dash, 0, 40, "‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ",
         bgcolor    = color.new(color.black, 60),
         text_color = color.new(color.gray, 40),
         text_size  = size.tiny)
    table.cell(dash, 1, 40, "‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ‚ĒĀ",
         bgcolor    = color.new(color.black, 60),
         text_color = color.new(color.gray, 40),
         text_size  = size.tiny)

    // ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Row 40: Version ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
    table.cell(dash, 0, 41, "VERSION",
         bgcolor     = color.new(color.black, 30),
         text_color  = color.silver,
         text_size   = size.tiny,
         text_halign = text.align_right)
    table.cell(dash, 1, 41, "AlphaEdge v6.5.3-r2",
         bgcolor    = color.new(color.black, 50),
         text_color = color.new(color.silver, 30),
         text_size  = size.tiny)

    // ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Row 41: Footer ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
    table.cell(dash, 0, 42, "AlphaEdge ¬© 2025",
         bgcolor    = color.new(color.black, 50),
         text_color = color.new(color.silver, 20),
         text_size  = size.small)
    table.cell(dash, 1, 42, "DYOR ¬∑ Not Financial Advice",
         bgcolor    = color.new(color.black, 50),
         text_color = color.new(color.silver, 20),
         text_size  = size.small)

// ============================================================================
//  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó     ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó
// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ     ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ
// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ     ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēĚ   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó
// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ     ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ   ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
// ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ   ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
// ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ  ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ  ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ   ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ   ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ
//  GRUB 8 ‚ÄĒ ALERTS ENGINE (v6.5.0 ‚ÄĒ Fixed, Upgraded, Perfected)
// ============================================================================
// Seluruh alert menggunakan `alert()` (bukan `alertcondition`) agar pesan
// dapat menyertakan nilai dinamis (signalTier, score, price, entryPrice, dll).
//
// Arsitektur:
//   SECTION 1 : Entry Signals   ‚ÄĒ longCondition / shortCondition
//   SECTION 2 : Take Profit     ‚ÄĒ TP1 (50%) dan TP2 (30%) per sisi
//   SECTION 3 : Stop Loss       ‚ÄĒ SL / Trail triggered per sisi
//   SECTION 4 : Market Structure‚ÄĒ BOS / CHoCH bullish & bearish
//   SECTION 5 : FVG             ‚ÄĒ Fair Value Gap bullish & bearish
//   SECTION 6 : Liquidity Sweep ‚ÄĒ Bull & Bear sweep (+ konfirmasi volume)
//   SECTION 7 : Divergence      ‚ÄĒ Bullish & Bearish (Regular + Hidden)
//   SECTION 8 : TC1D Volume     ‚ÄĒ TC 1D Bull & Bear volume signals
//   SECTION 9 : Oscillator Matrix ‚ÄĒ Bull & Bear multi-osc confirmation
//   SECTION 10: Breakeven       ‚ÄĒ Rising-edge saat SL digeser ke breakeven
//   SECTION 11: Hold Signals    ‚ÄĒ Rising-edge LONG HOLD & SHORT HOLD
//
// Guard / Anti-spam:
//   ‚ÄĘ Semua alert menggunakan `alert.freq_once_per_bar_close` ‚Üí maksimal
//     satu kali per bar pada penutupan bar, tidak spam per tick.
//   ‚ÄĘ TP alerts dijaga oleh `alertTP1SentLong/Short` & `alertTP2SentLong/Short`
//     (var bool, direset saat entry baru di Grub 5) ‚Üí tidak bisa duplikat
//     dalam satu posisi.
//   ‚ÄĘ BOS, CHoCH, FVG, LiqSweep, Divergence hanya fire saat
//     `barstate.isconfirmed` ‚Üí mencegah false alert di bar aktif (repainting).
//   ‚ÄĘ Breakeven & Hold menggunakan rising-edge (not prev*) ‚Üí fire satu kali
//     saat transisi false‚Üítrue, tidak berulang.
//   ‚ÄĘ SL alert dijaga `not na(currentDynamicSL)` ‚Üí tidak fire saat SL belum
//     terdefinisi (awal chart / sebelum ada posisi).
// ============================================================================

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 1 ‚ÄĒ ENTRY SIGNALS (LONG & SHORT)
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Menggunakan `alert()` karena pesan mengandung signalTier (string dinamis)
// dan score (integer dinamis). `alertcondition` tidak mendukung pesan dinamis.
// Informasi lengkap: ticker, tier, score, dan close price.
// ============================================================================

if longCondition and i_alertBuy
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüĒ• BUY [" + signalTier + "] on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Score: "           + str.tostring(bullScore)               +
         " | TF: "              + timeframe.period                      +
         " | Close: "           + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if shortCondition and i_alertSell
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ‚ĚĄÔłŹ SELL [" + signalTier + "] on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Score: "            + str.tostring(bearScore)               +
         " | TF: "               + timeframe.period                      +
         " | Close: "            + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 2 ‚ÄĒ TAKE PROFIT ALERTS (TP1 & TP2, LONG & SHORT)
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Guard `alertTP1SentLong/Short` dan `alertTP2SentLong/Short` (var bool)
// memastikan alert hanya terkirim satu kali per posisi.
// Guard-guard ini direset ke false oleh Grub 5 setiap kali entry baru.
// Catatan: `inLong`/`inShort` digunakan sebagai safety check tambahan agar
// alert tidak terkirim setelah posisi sudah ditutup namun flag masih true.
// ============================================================================

if inLong and tp1hitLong and not alertTP1SentLong and i_alertTP
    alertTP1SentLong := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ‚úÖ LONG TP1 (50%) hit on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Entry: "  + str.tostring(math.round(entryPrice, 4)) +
         " | TP1: "    + str.tostring(math.round(tp1, 4)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if inLong and tp2hitLong and not alertTP2SentLong and i_alertTP
    alertTP2SentLong := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüéĮ LONG TP2 (30%) hit on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Entry: "  + str.tostring(math.round(entryPrice, 4)) +
         " | TP2: "    + str.tostring(math.round(tp2, 4)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if inShort and tp1hitShort and not alertTP1SentShort and i_alertTP
    alertTP1SentShort := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ‚úÖ SHORT TP1 (50%) hit on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Entry: "  + str.tostring(math.round(entryPrice, 4)) +
         " | TP1: "    + str.tostring(math.round(tp1, 4)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if inShort and tp2hitShort and not alertTP2SentShort and i_alertTP
    alertTP2SentShort := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüéĮ SHORT TP2 (30%) hit on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Entry: "  + str.tostring(math.round(entryPrice, 4)) +
         " | TP2: "    + str.tostring(math.round(tp2, 4)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// TP3: full close by final trail/limit exit.
// Tidak ada state khusus di engine, jadi determinasi menggunakan prior TP1/TP2 hit
// dan penutupan harga di level TP3.
tp3ExitLong  = barstate.isconfirmed and longJustClosed  and tp1hitLong  and tp2hitLong  and not longClosedByReversal  and close > entryPrice
tp3ExitShort = barstate.isconfirmed and shortJustClosed and tp1hitShort and tp2hitShort and not shortClosedByReversal and close < entryPrice

if tp3ExitLong and not alertTP3SentLong and i_alertTP
    alertTP3SentLong := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüŹĀ LONG TP3 (20%) hit on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Entry: "  + str.tostring(math.round(entryPrice, 4)) +
         " | TP3: "    + str.tostring(math.round(tp3, 4)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if tp3ExitShort and not alertTP3SentShort and i_alertTP
    alertTP3SentShort := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüŹĀ SHORT TP3 (20%) hit on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Entry: "  + str.tostring(math.round(entryPrice, 4)) +
         " | TP3: "    + str.tostring(math.round(tp3, 4)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 3 ‚ÄĒ STOP LOSS / TRAIL TRIGGERED
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Guard `not na(currentDynamicSL)` mencegah false alert sebelum SL terdefinisi
// (mis. di awal chart atau sebelum ada posisi aktif).
// `barstate.isconfirmed` memastikan alert hanya fire di bar closed, bukan
// pada setiap tick intrabar yang belum final.
// ============================================================================

if longJustClosed and not longClosedByReversal and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertSL and not alertSLSentLong and
     not tp3ExitLong
    alertSLSentLong := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüõĎ LONG SL/Trail triggered on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Exit price: " + str.tostring(f_pricePrecision(close)) +
         " | Entry: " + str.tostring(f_pricePrecision(entryPrice)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if shortJustClosed and not shortClosedByReversal and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertSL and not alertSLSentShort and
     not tp3ExitShort
    alertSLSentShort := true
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüõĎ SHORT SL/Trail triggered on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Exit price: " + str.tostring(f_pricePrecision(close)) +
         " | Entry: " + str.tostring(f_pricePrecision(entryPrice)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 4 ‚ÄĒ MARKET STRUCTURE: BOS / CHoCH
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// `barstate.isconfirmed` wajib: BOS & CHoCH dihitung dari pivot yang baru
// terkonfirmasi. Tanpa guard ini alert dapat fire di bar aktif sebelum
// pivot benar-benar valid (repainting false-positive).
// ============================================================================

if (bosUp or chochUp) and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertBOS
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüďą Bullish " + (bosUp ? "BOS" : "CHoCH") +
         " on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if (bosDown or chochDown) and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertBOS
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüďČ Bearish " + (bosDown ? "BOS" : "CHoCH") +
         " on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 5 ‚ÄĒ FAIR VALUE GAP (FVG)
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// FVG dideteksi dari 3-candle pattern. `barstate.isconfirmed` mencegah
// false detection pada bar yang masih berjalan.
// ============================================================================

if fvgBullDetect and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertFVG
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüü© Bullish FVG detected on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if fvgBearDetect and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertFVG
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüü• Bearish FVG detected on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 6 ‚ÄĒ LIQUIDITY SWEEP
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Alert dibedakan berdasarkan konfirmasi volume:
//   ‚ÄĘ liqSweepBullConf / liqSweepBearConf (sweep + volume spike) ‚Üí "CONFIRMED"
//   ‚ÄĘ liqSweepBull / liqSweepBear tanpa spike                    ‚Üí "Detected"
// `barstate.isconfirmed` wajib karena liquidity sweep berbasis pivot swing.
// ============================================================================

if liqSweepBull and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertLiqSweep
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüíß Bullish Liquidity Sweep " +
         (liqSweepBullConf ? "CONFIRMED (Vol‚úď)" : "Detected") +
         " on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if liqSweepBear and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertLiqSweep
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüíß Bearish Liquidity Sweep " +
         (liqSweepBearConf ? "CONFIRMED (Vol‚úď)" : "Detected") +
         " on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 7 ‚ÄĒ DIVERGENCE (REGULAR & HIDDEN)
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Pesan menyertakan total count oscillator yang mengkonfirmasi divergence
// (RSI + MACD + Stochastic ‚Üí max 3 per tipe).
// `barstate.isconfirmed` wajib: divergence berbasis pivot RSI/price yang
// baru valid setelah bar closed.
// ============================================================================

if (divBullReg or divBullHid) and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertDiv
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüďź Bullish Divergence (" +
         str.tostring(divBullRegCount + divBullHidCount) + " osc) on " +
         syminfo.ticker +
         (divBullReg ? " | Regular‚ÜĎ" : "") +
         (divBullHid ? " | Hidden‚ÜĎ"  : "") +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if (divBearReg or divBearHid) and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertDiv
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüďź Bearish Divergence (" +
         str.tostring(divBearRegCount + divBearHidCount) + " osc) on " +
         syminfo.ticker +
         (divBearReg ? " | Regular‚Üď" : "") +
         (divBearHid ? " | Hidden‚Üď"  : "") +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 8 ‚ÄĒ TC 1D VOLUME SIGNALS
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Hanya aktif jika input `i_showTC1D` dicentang (toggle visual sekaligus
// penjaga alert TC1D agar konsisten dengan preferensi user).
// `barstate.isconfirmed` wajib agar volume signal tidak firing di tengah bar.
// ============================================================================

if i_showTC1D and tc1dBull and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertTC1D
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüĒ• TC1D Bullish Volume Signal on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if i_showTC1D and tc1dBear and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertTC1D
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüßä TC1D Bearish Volume Signal on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 9 ‚ÄĒ OSCILLATOR MATRIX
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Fire saat ‚Č•2 dari 3 sub-oscillator (Hyper Wave, Smart Money Flow, RSI
// Reversal) serentak memberikan vote ke arah yang sama.
// `barstate.isconfirmed` mencegah flip-flop intrabar.
// ============================================================================

if oscBull and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertBuy
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ‚ö° Oscillator Matrix BULL (" +
         str.tostring(oscBullCount) + "/3) on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if oscBear and barstate.isconfirmed and i_alertSell
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ‚ö° Oscillator Matrix BEAR (" +
         str.tostring(oscBearCount) + "/3) on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 10 ‚ÄĒ BREAKEVEN ACTIVATED
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Rising-edge detection: alert hanya terkirim sekali saat `breakevenActive`
// bertransisi dari false ‚Üí true. `prevBreakevenActive` di-update di akhir
// Grub 5 (Section 13 ‚ÄĒ Persistent State Sync) setelah semua logika selesai,
// sehingga nilai "prev" tepat merepresentasikan state bar sebelumnya.
// Guard `not na(entryPrice)` mencegah edge-case NaN pada str.tostring().
// ============================================================================

if breakevenActive and not prevBreakevenActive and not na(entryPrice) and i_alertBreakeven
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüĒí Breakeven activated on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " @ " + str.tostring(f_pricePrecision(entryPrice)),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

// ============================================================================
// SECTION 11 ‚ÄĒ HOLD SIGNALS (LONG HOLD & SHORT HOLD)
// ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
// Rising-edge detection: alert hanya terkirim sekali saat longHold/shortHold
// bertransisi false ‚Üí true (bukan berulang setiap bar selama hold aktif).
// `prevLongHold` dan `prevShortHold` di-update di akhir Grub 5 (Section 13).
// ============================================================================

longHoldRisingEdge  = longHold  and not prevLongHold
shortHoldRisingEdge = shortHold and not prevShortHold

if longHoldRisingEdge and i_alertBuy
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüüĘ LONG HOLD on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Score: " + str.tostring(bullScore) +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)

if shortHoldRisingEdge and i_alertSell
    alert(
         "AlphaEdge: ūüĒī SHORT HOLD on " + syminfo.ticker +
         " | Score: " + str.tostring(bearScore) +
         " | Close: " + str.tostring(close),
         alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)